  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK162">
<l>viḻuppēṟṟi ṉaḵtoppa tillaiyār māṭṭu</l>
<l>maḻukkāṟṟi ṉaṉmai peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Amongst all attainable excellences there is none equal to that of being free from envy towords others.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
